    "content": "<p></p><div style=\"border: solid #ddd 2px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #eee; padding: 2px;\"><code><a href=\"https://dxr.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/source/content/base/public/nsISelection3.idl\" rel=\"custom\">content/base/public/nsISelection3.idl</a></code><span style=\"text-align: right; float: right;\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Interfaces/About_Scriptable_Interfaces\" style=\"color: #00cc00; font-weight: 700;\">Scriptable</a></span></div>\n<span style=\"padding: 4px 2px;\">\n\n<i>Please add a summary to this article.</i>\n</span>\n\n  <div style=\"height: 42px; position: relative; padding: 2px; width: auto;\">\n\n  <div style=\"top: 22px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute;\">1.0</div>\n  \n  <div style=\"top: 22px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute; left: 0px; text-align: right; float: right; width: 100%;\">66</div>\n  \n  <div style=\"height: 8px; top: 16px; background: #dd0000; left: 0px; position: absolute; width: 11.428571428571429%;\"></div>\n  \n<div style=\"height: 8px; top: 16px; left: 11.428571428571429%; background: #00dd00; position: absolute; width: 5.7142857142857135%;\" title=\"Introduced in Gecko 2.0 (Firefox 4 / Thunderbird 3.3 / SeaMonkey 2.1)\"></div>\n\n<div style=\"top: 0px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute; left: 0px; text-align: right; float: right; width: 11.428571428571429%;\">Introduced</div>\n<div style=\"top: 22px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute; left: 0px; text-align: right; float: right; width: 11.428571428571429%;\">Gecko 2.0</div>\n\n    <div style=\"height: 8px; top: 16px; left: 17.142857142857142%; background: #000000; position: absolute; width: 82.85714285714286%;\" title=\"Obsolete in Gecko 8.0 (Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5)\"></div>\n    \n  <div style=\"top: 0px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute; left: 0px; text-align: right; float: right; width: 17.142857142857142%;\">Obsolete</div>\n  \n  <div style=\"top: 22px; font-size: 11px; position: absolute; left: 0px; text-align: right; float: right; width: 17.142857142857142%;\">Gecko 8.0</div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #eee; padding: 2px;\">\nInherits from: <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM/Reference/Interface/nsISupports\" title=\"\">nsISupports</a></code>\n<span style=\"text-align: right; float: right;\">Last changed in Gecko 2.0 (Firefox 4 / Thunderbird 3.3 / SeaMonkey 2.1)</span></div>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"note\">\n<p>In <span title=\"(Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5)\">GeckoÂ 8.0</span> this Interface was merged into the <code><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM/Reference/Interface/nsISelection\" title=\"\">nsISelection</a></code> interface.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"Method_overview\" name=\"Method_overview\">Method overview</h2>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>void <a href=\"#modify()\">modify</a>(in DOMString alter, in DOMString direction, in DOMString granularity);</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"Methods\" name=\"Methods\">Methods</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"modify()\" name=\"modify()\">modify()</h3>\n\n<p>Modifies the selection. Note that the parameters are case-insensitive.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"eval\">void modify(\n  in DOMString alter,\n  in DOMString direction,\n  in DOMString granularity\n);\n</pre>\n\n<h6 id=\"Parameters\" name=\"Parameters\">Parameters</h6>\n\n<dl>\n <dt><code>alter</code></dt>\n <dd>Can be one of { \"move\", \"extend\" }\n <ul>\n  <li>\"move\" collapses the selection to the end of the selection and applies the movement direction/granularity to the collapsed selection.</li>\n  <li>\"extend\" leaves the start of the selection unchanged, and applies movement direction/granularity to the end of the selection.</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n <dt><code>direction</code></dt>\n <dd>Can be one of { \"forward\", \"backward\", \"left\", \"right\" }</dd>\n <dt><code>granularity</code></dt>\n <dd>Can be one of { \"character\", \"word\", \"line\", \"lineboundary\" }</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h2 id=\"See_also\" name=\"See_also\">See also</h2>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM/Reference/Interface/nsISelection\" title=\"\">nsISelection</a></code></li>\n</ul>",
